The Great British Bake Off

The Great British Bake Off (also called Bake Off or GBBO) is a British television baking competition.

The first series featured a different baking theme each week:

  1. Cakes
  2. Biscuits
  3. Bread
  4. Puddings
  5. Pastry
  6. Tea Party

In each episode, the amateur bakers are given three challenges based on that weeks theme:

  • A signature bake,
  • a technical challenge,
  • and a show-stopper.
